  "version": "1.2.0",
  "description": "State-by-state statistics for US farmers markets, CSAs, and farm stands \u2014 per-state counts plus SNAP/EBT acceptance, certified-organic share, and website coverage \u2014 derived from the USDA AMS Local Food Portal and refreshed 2026. v1.1 (2026-07-07): website-coverage correction \u2014 a USDA live-API state-filter bug had left 9 states without enrichment data; per-state website_pct is now accurate (national ~50%). v1.2 (2026-07-14): adds the RECORD-LEVEL dataset \u2014 all 8,863 deduplicated markets (name, location, coordinates, website, season, SNAP/organic and other attributes) as CSV + JSON. Record-level files exclude scraped third-party content and personal contact names/emails.",
